We’ve all experienced living and working in “the zone”—that sweet spot where you have the greatest strength and the greatest ease. But how do you achieve that level of focus and do your best work amid the hectic pace of modern life? This audio course teaches you how to transform your life from overwhelmed and exhausted to joyful, relaxed, energetic, and productive. Learn exactly how to escape the busyness treadmill you’re on and focus on what really matters to you. Discover pro tips for reducing stress, eliminating unnecessary clutter, and managing the “overwhelm” in your life so you can thrive at everything you put your mind to. This audiobook was created by Penguin Random House. We are pleased to host this content in our library.